To hide tracks in Logic click the '''H''' icon on top of the arrange window so that it is green. Then click the '''H''' icon ''on the track headers of the tracks you wish to hide''. Then go back to the '''H''' icon at the top of the arrange window and click it again. The designated tracks will be hidden. To have them reappear simply click the '''H''' icon at the top of the arrange window again. 


